{"tid":1938982,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"信報：難阻食肆營業 研出招禁拜山","createTime":"2020-03-23T01:48:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-24T08:54:04.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"101d716090814b7c696c9b5b92e685edea07a322","tid":1938982,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:48:35.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情於歐美一發不可收拾，西班牙進入緊急狀態，英法頒令關閉餐廳，德國及美國部分地區更實施宵禁令。曾說防疫工作「宜緊不宜鬆」的特首林鄭月娥，上周六公布多項新措施嚴控病毒倒灌；然而，港府現階段似乎無意效法歐美雷厲風行的做法，繼續讓食肆、酒吧及娛樂場所如常營業。眾高官以至行政長官暫時只打「開 ...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2411014\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2411014&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdAwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=8f1ac527\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2411014</a><br />\n<br />\n大意：全禁食肆，做唔到+大規模倒閉+啲人湧去街巿一樣死<br />\n可能禁堂食只俾外賣<br />\n可能禁清明拜山"},{"pid":"87b0a8dfc9c448b25c4f3bfacdac3350dcea8d5b","tid":1938982,"uid":348156,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:50:45.000Z","msg":"一早就要禁堂食啦，依家先講&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6dc6ee13c71d035b398b1a3161c6476e4f18632","tid":1938982,"uid":57674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:51:09.000Z","msg":"攬炒之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0487de17485dcdd5afcc3f81dd28b9e669094f","tid":1938982,"uid":8478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:52:10.000Z","msg":"緊急法去咗邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0a8261ee67d6dbba67652ac3b61d234e67b68a","tid":1938982,"uid":53466,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T01:52:1